SQL_STMT_U.val: Select * from (select b.boh_opdrachtnummer from :1 b where b.boh_datum_uitvoering <= ~2 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer > 0 AND (b.boh_status = 15 OR (((b.boh_status = 54 AND b.boh_aanmaken_overboeking = 0) OR b.boh_status = 56) AND (b.boh_opdrachttype= 'REBA' OR b.boh_opdrachttype= 'SWTC'))) AND b.boh_herkomst BETWEEN ~3 AND ~4 AND b.boh_product BETWEEN ~5 and ~6 AND b.boh_relatie BETWEEN ~7 and ~8 order by b.boh_opdrachtnummer :9) where rownum <=1

select count(*) from :1 b where b.boh_datum_uitvoering <= ~2 AND (b.boh_status = 15 OR (((b.boh_status = 54 AND b.boh_aanmaken_overboeking = 0) OR b.boh_status = 56) AND (b.boh_opdrachttype= 'REBA' OR b.boh_opdrachttype= 'SWTC'))) AND b.boh_herkomst BETWEEN ~3 AND ~4 AND b.boh_product BETWEEN ~5 and ~6 AND b.boh_relatie BETWEEN ~7 and ~8 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer BETWEEN ~9 AND ~10 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer > 0

select C.LAAGSTE_OPDRACHTNR,C.AANTAL_OPDRACHTEN,b1.boh_opdrachtnummer,b1.boh_datum_uitvoering from :1 b1, (select count(*)"AANTAL_OPDRACHTEN",min(b.boh_opdrachtnummer)"LAAGSTE_OPDRACHTNR", b.boh_relatie"RELATIE",b.boh_product"PRODUCT",b.boh_product_volgnr"PRODUCTVOLGNR" from :1 b where b.boh_datum_uitvoering <= ~2 AND (b.boh_status = 15 OR (((b.boh_status = 54 AND b.boh_aanmaken_overboeking = 0) OR b.boh_status = 56) AND (b.boh_opdrachttype= 'REBA' OR b.boh_opdrachttype= 'SWTC'))) AND b.boh_herkomst BETWEEN ~3 AND ~4 AND b.boh_product BETWEEN ~5 AND ~6 AND b.boh_relatie BETWEEN ~7 AND ~8 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer BETWEEN ~9 AND ~10 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer > 0 Group by b.boh_relatie,b.boh_product,b.boh_product_volgnr Having count(*)>1) C
where b1.boh_datum_uitvoering <= ~2 AND (b1.boh_status = 15 OR (((b1.boh_status = 54 AND b1.boh_aanmaken_overboeking = 0) OR b1.boh_status = 56) AND (b1.boh_opdrachttype= 'REBA' OR b1.boh_opdrachttype= 'SWTC'))) AND b1.boh_herkomst BETWEEN ~3 AND ~4 AND b1.boh_product = C.PRODUCT AND b1.boh_product_volgnr = C.PRODUCTVOLGNR AND b1.boh_relatie = C.RELATIE AND b1.boh_opdrachtnummer BETWEEN ~9 AND ~10 AND b1.boh_opdrachtnummer > 0

SQL_STMT_U.val: Select C.DATUM_UITVOERING,C.OPDRACHTNR From ( select nvl(w.wk_datum_1,b.boh_datum_uitvoering)"DATUM_UITVOERING", nvl(w.wk_waarde_1,b.boh_opdrachtnummer)"OPDRACHTNR" from :1 b left outer join :2 w on (w.wk_terminal = ~3 AND w.wk_soort = ~4 AND w.wk_categorie_1 = ~5 AND w.wk_categorie_2 = to_char(b.boh_opdrachtnummer)) where ~6=1 AND ( ~7 = 1 OR b.boh_datum_uitvoering <= ~8 AND b.boh_herkomst between ~9 AND ~10 AND b.boh_product between ~11 AND ~12 AND b.boh_relatie between ~13 AND ~14 ) AND (b.boh_status = 15 OR (((b.boh_status = 54 AND b.boh_aanmaken_overboeking = 0) OR b.boh_status = 56) AND ( b.boh_opdrachttype= 'REBA' OR b.boh_opdrachttype= 'SWTC'))) AND (~15=1 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer = ~16 OR b.boh_opdrachtnummer > 0 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer between ~16 AND ~17) AND not (exists (select * from :2 w2 where w2.wk_terminal = ~3 AND w2.wk_soort = ~4 AND w2.wk_categorie_1 = ~5 AND w2.wk_waarde_2 = b.boh_opdrachtnummer)) UNION select b.boh_datum_uitvoering"DATUM_UITVOERING",b.boh_opdrachtnummer"OPDRACHTNR" from :1 b where ~6=0 AND ( ~7 = 1 OR b.boh_datum_uitvoering <= ~8 AND b.boh_herkomst between ~9 AND ~10 AND b.boh_product between ~11 AND ~12 AND b.boh_relatie between ~13 AND ~14 ) AND (b.boh_status = 15 OR (((b.boh_status = 54 AND b.boh_aanmaken_overboeking = 0) OR b.boh_status = 56) AND (b.boh_opdrachttype= 'REBA' OR b.boh_opdrachttype= 'SWTC'))) AND (~15=1 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer = ~16 OR b.boh_opdrachtnummer > 0 AND b.boh_opdrachtnummer between ~16 AND ~17) AND not (exists (select * from :2 w2 where w2.wk_terminal = ~3 AND w2.wk_soort = ~4 AND w2.wk_categorie_1 = ~5 AND w2.wk_waarde_2 = b.boh_opdrachtnummer)) ) C Order by 1,2
